phrases: Jheese, how high is my battle power now?
Jheese, hurry up and tell me!
You see, unless your mind and body are united,
you cannot put out any great power!
Kuririn, Gohan, you can beat this guy now!
We just might be able to beat him like this!
For a moment, he seemed like he really was Father.
I- I know what you mean.
Okay, it will not happen this time.
You are going to face me!
You mean that lousy Vegeta is still around?
You expect such a wimpy attack to hurt me?
This body is supposed to have a power greater than 180,000!
Did not you hear what Goku said before?
You cannot use that body very well.
Why do not you just give up now?
You expect me, Ginyu- sama to give up!?
For someone such as yourself to even consider picking a fight with me...
Babble as much as you want!
How did you manage to hide yourself!?
There was not any reading on my Scouter!
You guys rely too much on your Scouters!
If you were to fight against those guys from Earth,
you would figure it out for yourself!
That is, assuming you do not die here first!
The Ginyu Special Corps is made up of only
the most super-elite warriors in the universe!
There is no way a monkey bastard such as you
could ever stand a chance against me!
So you say, but you are actually afraid of
my renewed battle power, are not you?
Take a good, long look, with your precious Scouter there.
Me? Afraid of a battle power such as yours, Vegeta?
Do you really think it was a malfunction?
Every time I recover from being near death, I grow stronger.
I have also overcome the limits of ordinary Saiyans,
and I am still getting stronger!
Actually, I have just now realized something-
This growth in power is not just due to some kind of gift that I have.
Which means, I must be getting very close to becoming one myself!
A Super Saiyan is the mightiest of all warriors,
Kakarrot may not be cold-hearted enough to become one,
We are really hitting our stride!
L- looks like we are going to beat him, huh, Kuririn- san?
How can I, Commander of the Ginyu Special Corps,
Sure enough, it was useless trying to stop you,
and now you have become tangled up in things better left untouched.
Goku, soon you will realize the hidden terror possessed by Freeza.
It is not too late, even now.
Depart from that planet as quickly as you can!
I- if Dende... can just make it to where they are...
You Namekians really are very stubborn.
You have absolutely no chance of winning.
I do not want to use my energy needlessly.
I wonder how much longer I will be able to view Namek's scenery.
I hope it is until Dende reaches the Earthlings.
W- when Grand Elder- sama dies, the Dragon Balls will also disappear.
Before that happens, I have to hurry and meet up with those people.
It is like suddenly, it seems like he is gotten much stronger.
Looks like he is starting to get used to my body.
I am not going to be pushed around by rubbish like you guys!
I have not done this by myself very much,
but there is got to be something good for me to say here...
Oh well, maybe I will just skip it this time and leap right into battle.
I- I- I was not finished yet!
I will not be beaten by that flimsy blast!
This one will be even harder!
H- how did you manage that in your condition!?
I- it is just like you are doing.
I am starting to get used to this body.
I am going to fight, too!
Y- you may have become partially used to it,
but you still cannot generate its full power.
We have got to eliminate him, before he completely masters my body.
With the three of us, we can beat him!
There is something strange about this, huh?
I- I feel the same way.
I- it is a little odd to think that I am about to attack my own body like this.
There is no way we are going to be beaten by a monkey bastard like you!
It does not change the fact that you are no longer a match for Vegeta- sama!
Now then, how about I show you my true power?
You did not have to go that far!
You just keep on spouting that soft-hearted nonsense of yours, Kakarrot!
You will never become a Super Saiyan!
I am the only one who has that capacity!
Have not you taken care of Ginyu yet?
All right then, I will dispose of him for you!
Once again, Ginyu's signature technique, the Body Change, bursts forth.
